Major changes in this fork include:
- English UI, prompts, and documentation.
- Local embedded KuzuDB graph storage replacing hosted graph-service assumptions.
- Anthropic API, OpenAI API, OpenAI-compatible API, and optional Codex CLI provider support.
- Docker/local development cleanup.
- Workbench/session/resource refactoring.
- Compatibility fixes for OpenAI-compatible local models, including Qwen-style reasoning output handling.

